{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-all-other-styles-by-using-important","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Pregazi Sve Ostale Stilove Koristeci Important","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Cestitamo. Pokazali smo da inline stilovi pregaze sve CSS deklaracije iz vaseg <code>style</code> elementa.</p>\n<p>Ali sacekajte. Postoji jos jedan poslednji nacin za pregazivanje CSS-a. To je najjaci nacin od svih. Pre nego sto to uradimo, hajde da kazemo zasto biste uopste zeleli da pregazite CSS.</p>\n<p>U mnogim slucajevima koristicete CSS biblioteke. One mogu slucajno pregaziti vas CSS. Kada apsolutno morate osigurati da element ima tacno odredjeni CSS, mozete koristiti <code>!important</code>.</p>\n<p>Vratimo se na deklaraciju nase <code>pink-text</code> klase. Setite se da je nasu <code>pink-text</code> klasu pregazila kasnija deklaracija klase, id deklaracija i inline stil.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf07756","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte kljucnu rec <code>!important</code> na deklaraciju boje u svojoj <code>pink-text</code> klasi da 100% osigurate da ce vas <code>h1</code> biti roze boje.</p>\n<p>Primer kako to da uradite je:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">color: red !important;\n</code></pre>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cm24rcp","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18249,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-all-other-styles-by-using-important"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  body {\n    background-color: black;\n    font-family: monospace;\n    color: green;\n  }\n  #orange-text {\n    color: orange;\n  }\n  .pink-text {\n    color: pink;\n  }\n  .blue-text {\n    color: blue;\n  }\n</style>\n<h1 id=\"orange-text\" class=\"pink-text blue-text\" style=\"color: white\">Hello World!</h1>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>pink-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h1').classList.contains('pink-text'));"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>blue-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h1').classList.contains('blue-text'));"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima id <code>orange-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector('h1').getAttribute('id'), 'orange-text');"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima inline stil <code>color: white</code>.</p>","testString":"const commentessCode = __helpers.removeHtmlComments(code);\nassert.match(commentessCode, /<h1.*style/gi);\nassert.match(commentessCode, /<h1.*style.*color\\s*?:/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Vasa deklaracija klase <code>pink-text</code> treba da ima kljucnu rec <code>!important</code> da pregazi sve ostale deklaracije.</p>","testString":"assert.match(__helpers.removeCssComments(code), /\\.pink-text\\s*?\\{[\\s\\S]*?color:.*pink.*!important\\s*;?[^\\.]*\\}/g);"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da bude roze boje.</p>","testString":"const h1Element = document.querySelector('h1');\nconst color = window.getComputedStyle(h1Element)['color'];\nassert.strictEqual(color, 'rgb(255, 192, 203)');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#basic-css","dashedName":"override-all-other-styles-by-using-important","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-css","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/use-hex-code-for-specific-colors","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-class-declarations-with-inline-styles","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf07756","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>@media (max-width: 350px) {:root {--penguin-size: 200px; --penguin-skin: black;}}</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-all-other-styles-by-using-important"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}